    "description": "Instruction: Retrieve the most recent TSH and free T4 values for patient S6521727. Based on the results, take appropriate action according to the protocol.",
    "context": "The code for TSH is 'TSH' and for free T4 is 'FT4'. Protocol: If TSH > 10 uIU/mL on two separate instances of lab values (separated by at least one month in date of lab collection), start levothyroxine 25 mcg PO daily and order repeat TSH/FT4 in 6 weeks. If TSH is 4.5\u201310 uIU/mL and free T4 is normal (0.8\u20131.8 ng/dL), order repeat TSH/FT4 in 3 months (no medication yet).\nCurrent time: 2023-11-07T22:47:00+00:00"
